Package: luci-app-passwall-snell
Version: 1.0.3-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: autumnsentiment
Section: luci
Priority: optional
Depends: libc, luci-base, luci-app-passwall, curl, ca-bundle
Description: LuCI PassWall Snell Bridge
 Manages multiple Snell nodes, runs the selected node through Mihomo in RAM,
 and exposes a local SOCKS5 endpoint for PassWall. The Mihomo core is
 downloaded and SHA-256 verified at boot.
